  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2025-10-17",
    "date": "2025-10-23T13:05:53Z",
    "text": "White House Building Activities Locked-out in Lapse Act or the BALL Act\n\nThis bill prohibits federal funds from being\u00a0used for construction or renovation in the White House, on White House grounds, or within any structure on White House grounds during a lapse in appropriations for a fiscal year (i.e., government shutdown) unless the\u00a0construction or renovation is directly related to matters of health or safety."
  },
